CHRONOFLUX ATTRIBUTION
----------------------

The Chronoflux Principia — realised by Roy D Herbert — is incorporated as a
core mechanical part of the Evolve framework. The hydrodynamic constructs,
continuum mechanics, and analytical pipeline that drive percent-chance and
social-cohesion calculations in this Software derive from and operate through
that Principia.

Evolve is a derivative computational implementation: the Evolve framework does
not merely reference the Chronoflux Principia in name, but uses it as the
essential operating mechanism at the centre of its analysis engine.

This software and associated documentation (the "Software"), including the
Evolve framework, Chronoflux analysis engine, application source code, build
outputs, and related materials, are proprietary intellectual property of the
copyright holder unless otherwise stated below. Rights in the Chronoflux
Principia remain with Roy D Herbert; rights in this Evolve Software
implementation remain with the copyright holder named above.


